From: Brandon Thompson <brandon.joseph.thompson@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 17 Jul 2026 21:14:18 -0700
Subject: Patch: Fix VoicePopout burning 20% cpu constantly.

VoiceSurface.open was hardcoded to true in VoicePopout.qml instead of
tracking root.open, so the mic-capture wave (and its cava subprocess)
starts the moment the component is created at shell boot -- regardless
of whether the dictation popout is ever actually shown. Silently
captures the mic and burns ~20%+ CPU every session.

diff --git a/ryoku/shell/quickshell/pill/popouts/VoicePopout.qml b/ryoku/shell/quickshell/pill/popouts/VoicePopout.qml
index c09cc6bc..fa8b5d9b 100644
--- a/ryoku/shell/quickshell/pill/popouts/VoicePopout.qml
+++ b/ryoku/shell/quickshell/pill/popouts/VoicePopout.qml
@@ -23,7 +23,7 @@ Item {
         anchors.fill: parent
         s: root.s
         off: root.off
-        open: true
+        open: root.open
         shown: true
         openProgress: 1
         openW: root.implicitWidth
-- 
